{"title_page": "1978 1. deild karla", "text_new": "The '''1978 season''' of '''[[1. deild karla (football)|1. deild karla]]''' was the 24th season of second-tier football in [[Iceland]]. It is notable for being the only season [[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lag Reykjav\u00edkur|KR]] have spent outside the [[\u00darvalsdeild|top tier]].\n\n==Standings==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=PR\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=KR|name_KR=[[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lag Reykjav\u00edkur|KR]]\n|team2=HAU|name_HAU=[[Haukar]]\n|team3=\u00cdB\u00cd|name_\u00cdB\u00cd=[[\u00cd\u00fer\u00f3ttabandalag \u00cdsafjar\u00f0ar|\u00cdB\u00cd]]\n|team4=\u00de\u00d3R|name_\u00de\u00d3R=[[\u00de\u00f3r Akureyri|\u00de\u00f3r A.]]\n|team5=REY|name_REY=[[Reynir Sandger\u00f0i|Reynir S.]]\n|team6=AUS|name_AUS=[[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lag Fjar\u00f0abygg\u00f0ar|Austri]]\n|team7=\u00deR\u00d3|name_\u00deR\u00d3=[[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lag Fjar\u00f0abygg\u00f0ar|\u00der\u00f3ttur N.]]\n|team8=FYL|name_FYL=[[Fylkir]]\n|team9=\u00c1RM|name_\u00c1RM=[[Gl\u00edmuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 \u00c1rmann|\u00c1rmann]]\n|team10=V\u00d6L|name_V\u00d6L=[[\u00cd\u00fer\u00f3ttaf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 V\u00f6lsungur|V\u00f6lsungur]]\n|win_KR=13|draw_KR=4|loss_KR=1|gf_KR=48|ga_KR=9\n|win_HAU=8|draw_HAU=5|loss_HAU=5|gf_HAU=28|ga_HAU=24\n|win_\u00cdB\u00cd=7|draw_\u00cdB\u00cd=6|loss_\u00cdB\u00cd=5|gf_\u00cdB\u00cd=31|ga_\u00cdB\u00cd=25\n|win_\u00de\u00d3R=7|draw_\u00de\u00d3R=6|loss_\u00de\u00d3R=5|gf_\u00de\u00d3R=18|ga_\u00de\u00d3R=16\n|win_REY=7|draw_REY=4|loss_REY=7|gf_REY=22|ga_REY=21\n|win_AUS=6|draw_AUS=6|loss_AUS=6|gf_AUS=17|ga_AUS=21\n|win_\u00deR\u00d3=7|draw_\u00deR\u00d3=4|loss_\u00deR\u00d3=7|gf_\u00deR\u00d3=25|ga_\u00deR\u00d3=30\n|win_FYL=7|draw_FYL=2|loss_FYL=9|gf_FYL=22|ga_FYL=23\n|win_\u00c1RM=5|draw_\u00c1RM=2|loss_\u00c1RM=11|gf_\u00c1RM=21|ga_\u00c1RM=33\n|win_V\u00d6L=2|draw_V\u00d6L=3|loss_V\u00d6L=13|gf_V\u00d6L=18|ga_V\u00d6L=48\n\n|col_P=green1|text_P=Promoted to [[1979 \u00darvalsdeild]]\n|result1=P|resul