://www.facebook.com/sandylamyilin/posts/2918289834857926?__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARAUTPi5jMhL84eh92Ih7Ov3ID6Eb3H-9-vRPaSASIByU9bBIijqPY0t7vGyugRJksiZkggRpi5XBIMQ-6abu0DOn_BeBxyz0iBm3hOftfBLOOV3A9IVR3X9BUIfrWJNeHSJutov3psQHmS80tmWeSbClOngkh2Dr2qfxQBgafKxwKVKdFblTxr3vrANTwvbaFkHRFGjq9FEeq2HbQGTm91W6iYoWlXiiH73dEt3BBQfvHXZytT3YGIJx-naPCh9T_YTYjRec4lBXg6ecsEtuc9YzjBR8QySGGB1hxKehbnp2Zr436zltBkxJK8keTH3ssDUJV7uSfDE4A2--uludw&__tn__=-R |date=6 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Sandy Lam |title=Sandy Lam Weibo post February 6, 2020 |url=https://m.weibo.cn/detail/4469025180030265}}</ref>\n\n==Discography==\n\n===Cantonese albums===\n*''[[Sandy Lam (album)|Sandy Lam]]'' ([[:zh:\u6797\u61b6\u84ee (\u6797\u61b6\u84ee\u5c08\u8f2f)|\u6797\u61b6\u84ee]]) \u2013 Released April 1985\n*''[[Anger (album)|Anger]]'' ([[:zh:\u653e\u7e31 (\u6797\u61b6\u84ee\u5c08\u8f2f)|\u653e\u7e31]]) \u2013 Released March 1986\n*''[[Sandy (Sandy Lam album)|Sandy]]'' ([[:zh:\u61b6\u84ee|\u61b6\u84ee]]) \u2013 Released February 1987\n*''[[Grey (Sandy Lam album)|Grey]]'' ([[:zh:\u7070\u8272 (\u6797\u61b6\u84ee\u5c08\u8f2f)|\u7070\u8272]]) \u2013 Released August 1987\n*''[[Ready (Sandy Lam album)|Ready]]'' \u2013 Released June 1988\n*''[[City Rhythm (Sandy Lam album)|City Project Part I \u2013 City Rhythm]]'' ([[:zh:\u90fd\u5e02\u89f8\u89ba Part I City Rhythm|\u90fd\u5e02\u89f8\u89ba Part I City Rhythm]]) \u2013 Released December 1988\n*''[[City Project Part I - City Rhythm Take Two]]'' (\u90fd\u5e02\u89f8\u89baPart I City Rhythm Take Two) EP \u2013 Released April 1989\n*''[[City Project Part II - Fuir La Cite]]'' ([[:zh:\u90fd\u5e02\u89f8\u89ba Part II \u9003\u96e2\u92fc\u7b4b\u68ee\u6797|\u90fd\u5e02\u89f8\u89ba Part II \u9003\u96e2\u92fc\u7b4b\u68ee\u6797]]) \u2013 Released 24 October 1989\n*''[[City Project - Dynamic Reaction]]'' (\u90fd\u5e02\u89f8\u89ba\u4e4b\u63a8\u642a) EP \u2013 Released April 1990\n*''[[City Project Part III - Faces And Places]]'' ([[:zh:\u90fd\u5e02\u89f8\u89ba Part III Fa